@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title SecureEnvelope 结构对象图
left to right direction

object "SecureEnvelope" as env <<Neutral>> {
  protocol_major = 1
  header_version = 1
  header_len = 76 + 4 * target_count + auth_tag_len
  payload_len = variable
  checksum = uint32 additive sum
}

object "Magic\nbytes 0..3" as magic <<Bulk>> {
  value = 'S' 'U' 'R' 'Y'
  purpose = frame sync
}

object "Fixed Header\nbytes 4..75" as fixed <<Control>> {
  protocol_major
  header_version
  flags
  header_len / payload_len
  qos_class
  message_family / message_type / schema_version
  session_id / message_id / correlation_id
  created_at_ms / ttl_ms
  source
  target meta
  security meta
}

object "Variable Header\nbytes 76..(header_len-1)" as variable <<Neutral>> {
  target_ids[target_count]
  auth_tag[auth_tag_len]
}

object "Payload\nbytes header_len..(header_len+payload_len-1)" as body <<StatePlane>> {
  schema binary body
  interpretation = message_family + message_type + schema_version
}

object "Checksum\nlast 4 bytes" as checksum <<Risk>> {
  uint32 additive sum
  range = magic .. payload end
}

env *-- magic
env *-- fixed
env *-- variable
env *-- body
env *-- checksum

note right of fixed
固定头总长度为 76 bytes，
其中 bytes 0..3 是 magic，
bytes 4..75 是其余固定头字段。
end note

note right of variable
只有两类变长内容：
target_ids 与 auth_tag。
因此 header_len 的推导必须可验证。
end note

note right of body
Payload 不允许靠 transport 或私有编号解释，
只能由 schema 标识三元组解释。
end note
@enduml
